Hey guys and gals! 

My name is Jedi Ranger Kendor, and while I am not new to the forum, I am knew to starting to actively post here all the time. 

I have decided to start posting on here my adventures of my career mode as the Mount Helena Space Agency, and I hope that you will all enjoy reading them. 

I just don't know if such a thing belongs in the primary KSP Fan Works sub forum, or does it go into Mission Reports?

Hello semi-new person.

That sounds like a mission report to me.
